        {
          "id": "5k6nj530wq",
          "type": "fill",
          "prompt": "<code><span class=\"blank\" data-answer=\"@Profile\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Profile</span></code> is an example of a conditional configuration. When you annotate a component with <code><span class=\"blank\" data-answer=\"@Profile\" contenteditable=\"false\">@Profile</span></code>, the component is initialized conditionally when a specified profile is active.",
